OL,3,CTwo thirds of parents support ban on
OL,4,Cchildren using social media
OL,6,FWatch Richard Payne's report
OL,8,FTwo thirds of parents in the South
OL,9,FWest say they would support a ban on
OL,10,Fchildren under the age of 16 using
OL,11,Fsocial media.
OL,13,FThe survey, conducted by Opinium for
OL,14,FITV News, also indicated that more
OL,15,Fthan half of parents think their
OL,16,Fchildren's mental health is being
OL,17,Fnegatively impacted by using social
OL,18,Fmedia on their smartphones.
