OL,3,CTwo thirds of parents support ban on
OL,4,Cchildren using social media
OL,6,FFor the past five years the John Cabot
OL,7,FAcademy has had a complete ban on the
OL,8,Fuse of mobile phones in any part of
OL,9,Fthe school, at any time of day.
OL,11,FChildren caught with a phone have the
OL,12,Fdevice confiscated, locked in the
OL,13,Foffice and not returned until home
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FThe school's senior principal, Kate
OL,17,FWillis, said the move has improved the
OL,18,Fpupils mental health and learning.
