OL,3,CTwo thirds of parents support ban on
OL,4,Cchildren using social media
OL,6,FShe said "That well understood routine
OL,7,Factually brings them real
OL,8,Fpsychological safety, and when they
OL,9,Ffeel safe they can then explore and
OL,10,Fdevelop themselves as individuals"
OL,12,F"It's well known, it's accepted, and
OL,13,Fit's supported by the parents."
OL,15,FDaisy Greenwell is the founder of the
OL,16,Fcampaign group Smartphone Free
OL,17,FChildhood. She set it up last year to
OL,18,Ftry to support families overwhelmed by
OL,19,Fthe devices.
