OL,3,CTwo thirds of parents support ban on
OL,4,Cchildren using social media
OL,6,FThe group now includes more 200,000
OL,7,Fparents.
OL,9,FDaisy said the adults must take
OL,10,Fresponsibility and set workable
OL,11,Fboundaries.
OL,13,FShe said "You don't have to go to a
OL,14,Ffull fat iPhone, you can start with
OL,15,Fsomething that's much simpler and
OL,16,Fsafer, and less addictive."
